 Hydras landed and his body seemed to bolt out fire from every vein.  He shot 
every weapon in his arsenal at the shields.  Proot transformed into Rodimus 
Prime and fired several shots. Destructor followed suit. "We must bring these 
sheilds down!" (hopefully they wont last forever)
